00:15:16,902 --> 00:15:19,270
And they hurt me.

338
00:15:19,305 --> 00:15:20,438
So cruelly.

339
00:15:20,473 --> 00:15:23,908
Oh, there was no other woman.

340
00:15:23,943 --> 00:15:25,276
(laughs)

