Victim was asphyxiated, likely
with ether or chloroform.

351
00:16:02,782 --> 00:16:04,649
Look under the scalp.

352
00:16:05,851 --> 00:16:07,085
Humor me.

353
00:16:08,587 --> 00:16:10,188
At the base of the skull

354
00:16:10,222 --> 00:16:12,957
