Dix.

455
00:20:49,190 --> 00:20:51,058
Hey...!

456
00:20:51,092 --> 00:20:53,627
What do we have here?

457
00:20:53,661 --> 00:20:57,798
Harvey Bullock, boy detective.

458
00:20:57,832 --> 00:20:59,066
Look at you up there, huh?

459
00:20:59,100 --> 00:21:00,133
